<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>数据库管理系统（</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>DBMS</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>）中的并发控制的任务是确保在多个事务同时存取数据库中同一数据时不破坏事务的隔离性和数据的一致性。</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;

 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>乐观锁（乐观并发控制）和</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>悲观锁（悲观并发控制）是并发控制主要采用的技术手段</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:11.5pt' lang=zh-CN>乐观锁</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>（</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>Optimistic</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> </span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>Lock</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>）在事务更新数据时，它会首先读取数据并记录版本信息，然后在写回数据时，检查版本信息是否发生变化，以判断是否有其他事务对数据进行了修改。如果版本一致，则顺利提交更新，如果版本冲突，则需要进行冲突解决，例如回滚事务、重试或放弃更新操作</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;

     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>Share Lock</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>）</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'><span
style='font-weight:bold'>注</span></p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>悲观锁通常用于写比较多的情况下（多写场景，竞争激烈），通过加锁保证数据的一致性，这样可以避免频繁失败和重试影响性能。</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>乐观锁通常于写较少的情况下（多读场景，竞争较少），通过检查防止数据冲突，以避免频繁加锁影响性能，提高并发性能</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US>&nbsp;</p>

<p style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<p style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<p style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:13.5pt'><span
style='font-weight:bold'>两段锁协议</span></p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>两段锁协议（</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>Two-Phase Locking
     Protocol</span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:
     12.0pt'>，</span><span style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>2PL</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>）是一种数据库事务并发控制算法，通过在事务执行过程中强制所有访问数据的操作按照特定顺序进行加锁和解锁，保证事务的串行化执行</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";
font-size:12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>两段锁协议是指在对任何数据进行读、写操作之前，事务首先要申请并获得对该数据的封锁，当释放一个封锁之后，事务不再申请和获得任何其他封锁</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>在两段锁协议下，整个事务分为两个阶段，前一个阶段为加锁，后一个阶段为解锁</span></li>
</ul>

  <p style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:11.5pt;

  <td style='border-style:solid;border-color:#A3A3A3;border-width:1pt;
  background-color:#E7E6E6;vertical-align:top;width:.9319in;padding:2.0pt 3.0pt 2.0pt 3.0pt'>
  <p style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:11.5pt;
  color:#212121'>收缩阶段</p>
  </td>
  <td style='border-style:solid;border-color:#A3A3A3;border-width:1pt;
  background-color:#E7E6E6;vertical-align:top;width:5.5743in;padding:2.0pt 3.0pt 2.0pt 3.0pt'>
  <p style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:11.5pt'>当事务释放了一个锁以后，事务进入解锁阶段，在解锁阶段，事务只能解锁，不能再加锁</p>
  <p style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:11.5pt;color:#212121'>&nbsp;</p>
  <p style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:11.5pt;
  color:#212121'>事务会释放所有持有的锁，在释放所有锁之前，事务不能获取任何新的锁</p>
  </td>
 </tr>
</table>

</div>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>两段锁协议保证了事务在提交前所持有的锁不会被释放，其他事务不能访问相同的数据，从而避免了数据冲突和不一致性。</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'><span
style='font-weight:bold'>注</span></p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>如果并发执行的所有事务都遵循两段锁协议，那么对这些事务的任何并发调度都是可串行化的</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";
font-size:12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>两段锁协议只能保证事务的可串行调度，而不能保证并行可调度。如果多个事务并发地访问同一组数据，并且没有按照特定的顺序获取锁，那么就有可能会产生死锁。</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<p style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<p style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<p style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:13.5pt'><span
style='font-weight:bold'>封锁协议</span></p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>在使用</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>排他锁（</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>Exclusive
     Lock</span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'
     lang=zh-CN>）和</span><span style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
     12.0pt' lang=en-US> </span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";
     font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>共享锁（</span><span style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";
     font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>Share Lock</span><span style='font-family:
     "Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>）对数据对象加锁时，还需要约定一些规则
     ，例如何时申请</span><span style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'
     lang=en-US> </span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";
     font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>排他锁（</span><span style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";
     font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>Exclusive Lock</span><span style='font-family:
     "Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>）或</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>共享锁（</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>Share Lock</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>）、持锁时间、何时释放等，这些规则为封锁协议（</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>Locking
     Protocol</span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:
     12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>）。</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>不同的封锁协议，在不同的程度上为并发操作的正确调度提供一定的保证。根据不同的规则，分为以下三种封锁协议</span></li>
</ul>
